		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#654fa2" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#654fa2">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/流灰之城的魔龙.assets/Image_15.png')" x="64" y="64">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔龙连续发射4枚火球，每枚造成<span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="442" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔龙伏地进行蓄力，在其周围产生3枚凝露，此时其身覆有<span textDecoration="underline">虚界护罩</span><span>；10s后吸收凝露并发动震地攻击，造成</span><span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害，爆炸还将扩散到凝露所在的位置。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/流灰之城的魔龙.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1391" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/流灰之城的魔龙.assets/Image_17.png')" x="719" y="713">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔龙进行右划攻击，其分别造成<span color="#ff9999">40%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="430" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处于魔龙侧方或后方时， 魔龙自身转一圈，造成<span color="#ff9999">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">魔龙朝前方扇形区域喷吐怨流焚火，持续造成<span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
